title: How to delete an old email address from my Samsung S21FE?
creator: bjdocc
content: I have an old email address still showing up (it defaults to it as auto-fill) when I try to send myself an email on my Samsung s21, and I can't figure out how to delete it from the Address Book.....the problem being that I can't FIND the address book on the phone....I've also tried long-pressing the bad address on an email, settings, everything.....can't get rid of it. Help!
